Daily AI Agent Tasks:
Each day, the AI should:

Review progress from previous day

Write Lua configuration code for that day's features

Test the changes by restarting QuickShell

Take screenshots to verify appearance

Document what was changed

Create backup before making major changes

Ask for feedback on what to adjust